channel.title: [PI] How to fill an interface with text
channel.description: I have this a book interface with line1 - line 29 on it and I want to make it say things, but first I have to clear the text right? Can some one help me?

item.title: [PI] How to fill an interface with text
item.dc:creator: @Ambokile Ambokile
item.description:
@Ambokile wrote:

Use sendFrame126 (or whatever your method is) with a loop between 1 and 10000 setting it to the integer and you’ll know which line to change.
